369
00:26:39,383 --> 00:26:41,097
All right, look, I got a first aid kit in my truck.

370
00:26:41,132 --> 00:26:42,021
Are you going to touch it?

371
00:26:43,468 --> 00:26:43,999
It may be dying.

372
00:26:44,685 --> 00:26:46,054
But, Russell, you don't know what that thing is.

373
00:26:46,089 --> 00:26:47,273
You don't know what it's going to do.

374
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,302
Larkin...

375
00:26:50,629 --> 00:26:51,353
Larkin, come here.

376
00:26:51,388 --> 00:26:52,230
No.

377
00:26:52,265 --> 00:26:53,256
No, no, no, come here.

378
00:26:54,246 --> 00:26:55,654
It's...it's trying to see you.

379
00:26:55,689 --> 00:26:57,100
I don't think he wants you to leave.

380
00:27:03,036 --> 00:27:03,798
It's okay, come here.

