385
00:27:19,021 --> 00:27:19,564
I don't know.

386
00:27:20,516 --> 00:27:22,419
All right, back up, back up. Okay...

387
00:27:24,437 --> 00:27:25,730
all right, all right, all rit, back, back, back.

388
