395
00:28:23,796 --> 00:28:25,013
The only reason I wanted to talk to him

396
00:28:25,048 --> 00:28:28,516
was to see what he knew, and he knows a lot.

397
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,837
It may lead to something...

398
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:33,957
but he didn't do this.

399
00:28:34,645 --> 00:28:35,252
Are you...

400
00:28:36,053 --> 00:28:37,158
