491
00:33:51,133 --> 00:33:51,552
Really?

492
00:33:53,886 --> 00:33:55,502
- He's my priest.
- No, I know.

493
00:33:56,349 --> 00:33:57,301
You saw him recently?

494
00:33:57,336 --> 00:34:01,553
- Did you talk about cutting off your...
