502
00:34:46,063 --> 00:34:46,790
Yeah, I won't.

503
00:34:51,434 --> 00:34:52,198
Russ...

504
00:35:00,537 --> 00:35:02,138
I hope our baby's like you.

505
00:35:04,122 --> 00:35:10,212
I hope that he or she is never afraid of what they don't understand.

506
00:35:29,876 --> 00:35:33,499
Oh, my god, I am heartily sorry for my sins,

507
00:35:35,776 --> 00:35:36,995
and I firmly resolve,

508
00:35:38,639 --> 00:35:43,281
with the help of thy grace, to confess my sins...

509
00:35:45,645 --> 00:35:46,328
to do penance...

510
00:35:48,839 --> 00:35:50,402
and to amend my life.

511
00:35:53,494 --> 00:35:54,142
I...

512
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:58,715
- Tom.
- It's all right, father.

513
00:36:01,152 --> 00:36:01,873
You're not alone.

514
00:36:07,162 --> 00:36:08,343
We both know it was you.

515
00:36:12,910 --> 00:36:13,518
What do you mean?

516
00:36:13,553 --> 00:36:14,511
Oh, come on, what,

517
00:36:14,546 --> 00:36:16,753
are you gonna make me start quoting passages of judas?

518
00:36:22,845 --> 00:36:23,873
Why would you want to kill me?

519
00:36:27,678 --> 00:36:30,154
You abuse the privilege of God's grace.

520
00:36:32,726 --> 00:36:35,961
You...you mutilated a man in the name of your own...

521
